	(10, '一加ace3重磅来袭', '站内新闻', '<div class="content5_xq17896_180426 red" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #333333; font-family: &quot;background-color:#FFFFFF;">\n<p style="font-size: 16px; color: #000000; text-indent: 2em; font-family: SimSun !important;"><span style="color: #333333; font-family: Arial, \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;">这是一加 Ace3「鸣沙金」，如沙漠中的一缕阳光。</span><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #333333; font-family: Arial, \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;" /><span style="color: #333333; font-family: Arial, \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;">低调且高级，浪漫与优雅，活力与平静，自信且从容。</span><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #333333; font-family: Arial, \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;" /><span style="color: #333333; font-family: Arial, \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;">行业首创「熔金玻璃工艺」，使玻璃质感与金属色泽恰到好处融合。「金属喷砂工艺」结合精密切削的3D曲线金属中框弧线，带来了舒适流畅的手感。</span><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #333333; font-family: Arial, \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;" /><span style="color: #333333; font-family: Arial, \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;">这一抹低调奢华的色彩，大家觉得怎么样?</span></p>\n<p style="font-size: 16px